That's not a problem to read, and it's really easy to recognize since everyone's been sent it at some point in their life.<p>For those having trouble:<p><pre><code>    bomb() {
      bomb | bomb &  # spawns two subprocesses, each running bomb
                     # on one end of a pipe, neither will die
                     # so long as the other exists
    }
    bomb             # kick off the bomb</code></pre>
